\[ f(x) = $pol \]
is decreasing on the interval ( \{ans_rule(5)\} , \{ans_rule(5) \}  ).
$BR$BR
It is increasing on the interval ( \(-\infty\), \{ans_rule(5) \} ) and the
interval ( \{ans_rule(5) \}, \(\infty \)  ).
$BR$BR
The function has a local maximum at \{ans_rule(10) \}.
END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp($a));
ANS(num_cmp($b));
ANS(num_cmp($a));
ANS(num_cmp($b));
ANS(num_cmp($a));

